{"tid":1426214,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"在那激光筆穿梭  我沒justuce Laws將你來鎖","createTime":"2019-08-07T01:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:15:49.000Z","uid":79055,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e11899edc357a782ed8e7d14a4d7009d85f72dc","tid":1426214,"uid":79055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"激光筆（激光中）<br />\n＊  光加熱就等於火　火加光就等傷我<br />\n     若我與再加上你　溫度將提高更多<br />\n     所以我應拘捕你　不要再自我封鎖<br />\n     此一刻你屬於我　你再也沒法擋　YEA<br />\n<br />\n＃   將今晚今晚交給我　我要為你柒盡更多<br />\n     施展我一身解數　在那激光筆穿梭<br />\n     我沒justuce Laws　將你來鎖<br />\n<br />\n＋   不管你是姓甚麼　也不管你是何星座<br />\n     只要你是有耳朵　佢便會令你瘋魔<br />\n     要與你發生捉摸　以好歌捉摸你心窩<br />\n     此一刻你屬於我　你再也沒法擋　YEA<br />\n<br />\n     歌聲似激光奔放　我發熱我發亮發光<br />\n     沖激你使你心火燙　在那身軀的確光<br />\n     與勁歌激光　搖擺搖蕩<br />\n<br />\n未改得哂，有冇人一齊改，要開工🙏🏻"},{"pid":"acc26500d7e7eb65219c94b1fee22530f6852cc6","tid":1426214,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7DSI7pvymrE/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F7DSI7pvymrE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6b73e978&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2aa30e5793eb8b433790d82682135e97fd4db9d","tid":1426214,"uid":128287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"好似筆轉做槍會好D"},{"pid":"9d98de3840f8073067987dfff08d65a42e78288d","tid":1426214,"uid":121911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:41:55.000Z","msg":"點解入香港警察？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊馬。<br />\n我唔妥你，我可以𢭃你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以𢱕你。<br />\n𡃁仔你睥咩呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？<br />\n你見過冧友未呀？你見過人買觀星筆未呀？<br />\n你話盧偉聰你偶像吖嘛，你見過盧偉聰未呀？<br />\n警務處處長吖嘛，好巴閉呀？<br />\n你知唔知佢can&rsquo;t find a right word, 佢掹唔到；<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢d o靚，打人，佢停唔到。<br />\n你知唔知盧偉聰諗緊咩呀？<br />\n話畀你聽佢唔想做處長，<br />\n佢唔想講英文，<br />\n但係佢冇辦法，冇得返轉頭。<br />\n係呀，每個人都有偶像，我都有。<br />\n其實，讀唔讀書，我理唔到咁多，<br />\n但係我想話畀你聽，行錯路，冇得返轉頭。"},{"pid":"8baf8e024e97b7ca61fb04d38428a9c0a30b149c","tid":1426214,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745a266725fa0086065d253757a91e5809170301","tid":1426214,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"唔理basic law 將你來鎖<br />\n咁得唔得"},{"pid":"ce7cfb77138b0d7341b800425c96e57ce7a324bc","tid":1426214,"uid":65091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"745a266725fa0086065d253757a91e5809170301","tid":1426214,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"唔理basic law 將你來鎖<br />\n咁得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:47:59.000Z","msg":"伍利basic law, 你唱一次睇下o唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8a188416e5fa97c8e5ef103528edd813e8891f","tid":1426214,"uid":274180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"就算揸粒乒乓波 我話好驚慌 中意就鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5642303e481f4fa9d4e22e518a0a98a57fd301","tid":1426214,"uid":159878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd230c1737af9210e1646c4c9e41242c42d28743","tid":1426214,"uid":182001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid"